      },
      {
        "featureType": "OTHER",
        "additionalInfo": "What is Lenders Mortgage Insurance? Also known as LMI, this is insurance that generally protects the lender in the event you default on your repayments. This insurance is required if you're borrowing more than 80% of the property value.",
